550  /*   |///////|///////|///////|       |       | */



551  /*    _______________________________________  */



552  /*   |///////|///////|///////|       |       | */



553  /*  2|/(2,0)/|/(2,1)/|/(2,2)/| (2,3) | (2,4) | */



554  /*   |///////|///////|///////|       |       | */



555  /*    _______________________________________  */



556  /*   |       |       |       |       |       | */



557  /*  3| (3,0) | (3,1) | (3,2) | (3,3) | (3,4) | */



558  /*   |       |       |       |       |       | */



559  /*    _______________________________________  */



560  /*   |       |       |       |       |       | */



561  /*  4| (4,0) | (4,1) | (4,2) | (4,3) | (4,4) | */



562  /*   |       |       |       |       |       | */



563  /*    ---------------------------------------  */



564  vipldws_B.o[0U] = 0;



565  vipldws_B.o[1U] = 1;



566  vipldws_B.o[2U] = 2;



567  vipldws_B.o[3U] = 3;



568  vipldws_B.o[4U] = 4;



569  isEnd = false;



570  vipldws_B.c[1U] = 0;



571



572  /* if hDims < uDims then the all INSIDE sector will not be pushed into the boundary sectors... hence the counter needs to skip the all INSIDEs sector and start from one sector down. */



573  vipldws_B.c[0U] = 1;



574  while (!isEnd) {



575    uOrigin = 0;



576    yPost = 0;



577



578    /* compute on-boundary sector */



579    /* compute sector if not empty */



580    if (!((vipldws_B.mWidth[vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0U]] << 1] <= 0) ||



581          (vipldws_B.mWidth[(vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1U]] << 1) + 1] <= 0))) {



582      /* compute sector for this dim */



583      /* sector start corresponds to margin loc */



584      /* apply offset of margin width for sector end */



585      /* Inside Sector if 0 in all dimensions */



586      isSEmpty = (vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] == 0);



587      dimIsPre = ((vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] == 3) ||



588                  (vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] == 1));



589      if (dimIsPre || isSEmpty) {



590        vipldws_B.sPreEdges[0] = 0;



591        uOrigin = 1;



592      }



593



594      if ((!(dimIsPre || isSEmpty)) || isSEmpty) {



595        vipldws_B.sPostEdges[0] = 0;



596        yPost = 1;



597      }



598



599      /* compute sector for this dim */



600      /* sector start corresponds to margin loc */



601      /* apply offset of margin width for sector end */



602      /* Inside Sector if 0 in all dimensions */



603      isSEmpty = (vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] == 0);



604      dimIsPre = ((vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] == 3) ||



605                  (vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] == 1));



606      if (dimIsPre || isSEmpty) {



607        vipldws_B.sPreEdges[uOrigin] = 1;



608        uOrigin++;



609      }



610



611      if ((!(dimIsPre || isSEmpty)) || isSEmpty) {



612        vipldws_B.sPostEdges[yPost] = 1;



613        yPost++;



614      }



615



616      /* setup indices for the loops */



617      /* Origin stores the origin of Y with respect to U */



618      /*  where the origin of Y is at its top left corner */



619      /* Compute offset between origin of Y and origin of U(0,0) */



620      vipldws_B.offset[0U] = -yOrigin[0U];



621      vipldws_B.offset[1U] = -yOrigin[1U];



622



623      /* sector start and end were computed relative to U */



624      /* make them relative to Y by adding offset */



625      vipldws_B.sStart[0U] = vipldws_B.mLoc[vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] << 1] +



626        vipldws_B.offset[0U];



627      vipldws_B.sEnd[0U] = ((vipldws_B.mLoc[vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] << 1] +



628        vipldws_B.mWidth[vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[0]] << 1]) + vipldws_B.offset



629                            [0U]) - 1;



630      vipldws_B.sStart[1U] = vipldws_B.mLoc[(vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] << 1) +



631        1] + vipldws_B.offset[1U];



632      vipldws_B.sEnd[1U] = ((vipldws_B.mLoc[(vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] << 1) +



633        1] + vipldws_B.mWidth[(vipldws_B.o[vipldws_B.c[1]] << 1) + 1]) +



634                            vipldws_B.offset[1U]) - 1;



635



636      /* adjust offset for kernel center */



637      vipldws_B.offset[0U] -= hLoc[0U];



638      vipldws_B.offset[1U] -= hLoc[1U];



639



640      /* loop kernel over data */



641      vipldws_B.idxB[1U] = vipldws_B.sStart[1U];



642      while (vipldws_B.idxB[1U] <= vipldws_B.sEnd[1U]) {



643        vipldws_B.idxA[1U] = vipldws_B.idxB[1U] - vipldws_B.offset[1U];



644        vipldws_B.idxBLin_c[1U] = yDims[0U] * vipldws_B.idxB[1U];



645        vipldws_B.idxB[0U] = vipldws_B.sStart[0U];



646        while (vipldws_B.idxB[0U] <= vipldws_B.sEnd[0U]) {



647          vipldws_B.idxA[0U] = vipldws_B.idxB[0U] - vipldws_B.offset[0U];



648          vipldws_B.idxBLin_c[0U] = vipldws_B.idxBLin_c[1U] + vipldws_B.idxB[0U];



649



650          /* loop over kernel and compute conv/corr */



651          hPost = 0;



652          acc = 0.0F;



653



654          /* loop over kernel */



655          vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[1U] = 0;



656          while (vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[1U] <= vipldws_B.hEnd[1U]) {



657            vipldws_B.hIdxB[1U] = vipldws_B.idxA[1U] + vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[1U];



658            vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[0U] = 0;



659            while (vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[0U] <= vipldws_B.hEnd[0U]) {



660              vipldws_B.hIdxB[0U] = vipldws_B.idxA[0U] + vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[0U];



661              uI = PadBRepl_uS(&u[0U], &vipldws_B.uStride[0U], &vipldws_B.hIdxB



662                               [0U], &vipldws_B.uOrigin[0U], &vipldws_B.uEnd[0U],



663                               uOrigin, &vipldws_B.sPreEdges[0U], yPost,



664                               &vipldws_B.sPostEdges[0U]);



665              acc += uI * h[hPost];



666              hPost++;



667              vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[0U]++;



668            }



669



670            vipldws_B.hIdxA_k[1U]++;



671          }



672



673          if (vipldws_B.idxBLin_c[0U] >= 0) {



674            y[vipldws_B.idxBLin_c[0U]] = acc;



675          }



676



677          vipldws_B.idxB[0U]++;



678        }



679



680        vipldws_B.idxB[1U]++;



681      }



682    }



683



684    /* advance sector counter */



685    uOrigin = 0;



686    while (uOrigin < 2) {



687      vipldws_B.c[uOrigin]++;



688      if (vipldws_B.c[uOrigin] <= 2) {



689        isEnd = false;



690        uOrigin = 2;



691      } else {



692        vipldws_B.c[uOrigin] = 0;



693        isEnd = true;



694      }



695



696      uOrigin++;



697    }



698  }



699



700  /* End of S-Function (svip2dfirfilter): '<S3>/2-D FIR Filter' */



701}



702



703int8_T rt_sqrt_Us8_Ys4_Is8_f_pw(int8_T u)



704{



705  int8_T y;



706  int8_T tmp01_y;



707



708  /* Fixed-Point Sqrt Computation by the bisection method. */



709  if (u > 0) {



710    y = 0;



711    if (16 <= u) {



712      y = 4;



713    }



714



715    tmp01_y = (int8_T)(y | 2);



716    if (tmp01_y * tmp01_y <= u) {



717      y = tmp01_y;



718    }



719



720    tmp01_y = (int8_T)(y | 1);



721    if (tmp01_y * tmp01_y <= u) {



722      y = tmp01_y;



723    }



724  } else {



725    y = 0;



726  }



727



728  return y;



729}



730



731real32_T rt_roundf_snf(real32_T u)



732{



733  real32_T y;



734  if ((real32_T)fabs(u) < 8.388608E+6F) {



735    if (u >= 0.5F) {



736      y = (real32_T)floor(u + 0.5F);



737    } else if (u > -0.5F) {



738      y = u * 0.0F;



739    } else {



740      y = (real32_T)ceil(u - 0.5F);



741    }



742  } else {



743    y = u;



744  }



745



746  return y;



747}



748



749void LDLf_int32_Treal32_T(real32_T out[], real32_T vArray[], int32_T nRows,



750  const real32_T in[])



751{



752  int32_T c;



753  int32_T r;



754  int32_T idx1;



755  int32_T idx2;



756  real32_T mYTmp;



757  real32_T mYTmpR;



758  boolean_T done;



759  int32_T k;



760



761  /* S-Function (sdspldl2): '<S46>/LDL Factorization' */



762  done = false;



763



764  /* use done to control the for loop return early  */



765  /* when non-positive definite eigenvalue is detected */



766  c = 0;



767  while ((c < nRows) && (!done)) {



768    idx2 = c * nRows;



769    for (r = 0; r < c; r++) {



770      idx1 = r * nRows;



771      vArray[r] = out[idx1 + c] * out[idx1 + r];



772    }



773



774    mYTmp = in[idx2 + c];



775    idx1 = c;



776    for (r = 0; r < c; r++) {



777      mYTmp -= out[idx1] * vArray[r];



778      idx1 += nRows;



779    }



780



781    mYTmpR = mYTmp;



782    if (mYTmp <= 0.0F) {



783      done = true;



784    } else {



785      out[idx2 + c] = mYTmp;



786      for (r = c + 1; r < nRows; r++) {



787        mYTmp = in[idx2 + r];



788        idx1 = r;



789        for (k = 0; k < c; k++) {



790          mYTmp -= out[idx1] * vArray[k];



791          idx1 += nRows;



792        }



793



794        out[idx2 + r] = mYTmp / mYTmpR;



795      }



796    }



797



798    c++;



799  }



800



801  /* transpose and copy lower sub-triang to upper */



802  c = 0;



803  while ((c < nRows) && (!done)) {



804    for (r = c + 1; r < nRows; r++) {



805      out[r * nRows + c] = out[c * nRows + r];



806    }



807



808    c++;



809  }



810



811  /* End of S-Function (sdspldl2): '<S46>/LDL Factorization' */



812}



813



814/* Model step function */



815void vipldws_step(void)



816{



817  boolean_T c_gotAlLeastOneYellowPixelInThe;



818  boolean_T prevEdgeIsVertical;



819  int8_T idxTmpArray[2];



820  boolean_T countTwice;



821  int8_T idxTmpArray_0[2];



822  boolean_T done;



823  static const int8_T tmp[4] = { 1, 0, 3, 2 };



824



825  static const int8_T tmp_0[12] = { 1, 0, 3, 2, 5, 4, 7, 6, 9, 8, 11, 10 };



826



827  int8_T acc4_idx_0;



828  int8_T acc1_idx_1;



829  int8_T acc1_idx_5;



830  int8_T lineColorIdx_idx_0;



831  int8_T solidBrokenIdx_idx_0;



832  int32_T exitg1;



833



834  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



835  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.SampleandHold_SubsysRanBC);



836



837  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



838  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Enablesignalgenerator_SubsysRan);



839



840  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



841  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Core_SubsysRanBC);



842



843  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



844  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Options_SubsysRanBC);



845



846  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



847  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Differencebetweentwolines_Subsy);



848



849  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



850  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Selectalinefromtherepositoryifi);



851



852  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



853  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Draw3rdLine_SubsysRanBC);



854



855  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



856  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.DrawPolygon_SubsysRanBC);



857



858  /* Reset subsysRan breadcrumbs */



859  srClearBC(vipldws_DW.Subsystem_SubsysRanBC);



860



861  /* S-Function (v4l2_video_capture_sfcn): '<S2>/V4L2 Video Capture' */



862  MW_videoCaptureOutput(vipldws_ConstP.V4L2VideoCapture_p1,



863                        &vipldws_B.MatrixConcatenate[0],



864                        &vipldws_B.MatrixConcatenate[76800],



865                        &vipldws_B.MatrixConcatenate[153600]);



866



867  /* S-Function (svipscalenconvert): '<S2>/Image Data Type Conversion' */



868  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 230400; vipldws_B.i++) {



869    vipldws_B.ImageDataTypeConversion[vipldws_B.i] = (real32_T)



870      vipldws_B.MatrixConcatenate[vipldws_B.i] / 255.0F;



871  }



872



873  /* End of S-Function (svipscalenconvert): '<S2>/Image Data Type Conversion' */



874



875  /* S-Function (svipcolorconv): '<S2>/Color Space  Conversion' */



876  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 76800; vipldws_B.i++) {



877    vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i] =



878      (vipldws_B.ImageDataTypeConversion[76800 + vipldws_B.i] * 0.587F +



879       vipldws_B.ImageDataTypeConversion[vipldws_B.i] * 0.299F) +



880      vipldws_B.ImageDataTypeConversion[153600 + vipldws_B.i] * 0.114F;



881    if (vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i] > 1.0F) {



882      vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i] = 1.0F;



883    } else {



884      if (vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i] < 0.0F) {



885        vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i] = 0.0F;



886      }



887    }



888  }



889



890  /* End of S-Function (svipcolorconv): '<S2>/Color Space  Conversion' */



891



892  /* S-Function (sdspsubmtrx): '<S2>/Clip image' */



893  vipldws_B.yIdx = 0;



894  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 240; vipldws_B.i++) {



895    memcpy(&vipldws_B.Clipimage[vipldws_B.yIdx],



896           &vipldws_B.ColorSpaceConversion[vipldws_B.i * 320 + 120], 200U *



897           sizeof(real32_T));



898    vipldws_B.yIdx += 200;



899  }



900



901  /* End of S-Function (sdspsubmtrx): '<S2>/Clip image' */



902



903  /* S-Function (svip2dfirfilter): '<S3>/2-D FIR Filter' */



904  /* Dimensions of the filter */



905  vipldws_B.h1Dims[0U] = 1;



906  vipldws_B.h1Dims[1U] = 3;



907  vipldws_B.uDims[0U] = 200;



908  vipldws_B.uDims[1U] = 240;



909



910  /* set up kernel related coordinates */



911  /* compute center */



912  /* hLoc is the location of top left corner relative to the center of kernel. */



913  vipldws_B.hLoc[0U] = 0;



914



915  /* compute center */



916  /* hLoc is the location of top left corner relative to the center of kernel. */



917  vipldws_B.hLoc[1U] = -1;



918



919  /* Region of Support (ROS) definition: A selected region that restricts the input space for processing. */



920  /* ====================================================== */



921  /*                       ---------------------            */



922  /*                      |ROI                  |           */



923  /*                      |                     |           */



924  /*  ----------------------------------------------------  */



925  /* | INPUT(u)           |                     |         | */



926  /* |                    |                     |         | */



927  /* |   ---------------------------------------------    | */



928  /* |  | ROS             |OUTPUT(y)////////////|     |   | */



929  /* |  |                 |/////////////////////|     |   | */



930  /* |  |                  ---------------------      |   | */



931  /* |  |                                             |   | */



932  /* The user's output mode choices of 'Valid', 'Same as input' and 'Full' map onto correspending definitions of a rectangular ROS. */



933  /* Output range support is computed as an intersection of ROS with Region of Interest (ROI) */



934  /* ///////////////////// */



935  /* begin ROS computation */



936  /* compute ROS based on u, h and output mode */



937  /* ROS is SAME AS INPUT */



938  /* end ROS computation */



939  /* /////////////////// */



940  /* ///////////////////////// */



941  /* begin y sizes computation */



942  /* we need to compute yOrigin and yEnd */



943  /* yOrigin definition: Location of center of reference (origin) of output (y) coordintate system with respect to input (u) coordinate system */



944  /* y sizes are same as ros sizes because there is no ROI */



945  vipldws_B.yOrigin[0U] = 0;



946  vipldws_B.yDims[0U] = 200;



947



948  /* y sizes are same as ros sizes because there is no ROI */



949  vipldws_B.yOrigin[1U] = 0;



950  vipldws_B.yDims[1U] = 240;



951



952  /* make yOrigin same as roiLoc when y is empty */



953  /* end y sizes computation */



954  /* /////////////////////// */



955  vipldws_Corr_M_IBRepl_uS_hS_yS(&vipldws_P.uDFIRFilter_filterMtrx[0U],



956    &vipldws_B.hLoc[0U], &vipldws_B.h1Dims[0U], &vipldws_B.Clipimage[0U],



957    &vipldws_B.uDims[0U], &vipldws_B.uDFIRFilter[0U], &vipldws_B.yDims[0U],



958    &vipldws_B.yOrigin[0U]);



959



960  /* Saturate: '<S3>/Saturation' */



961  /* check if any input is empty



962   */



963  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 48000; vipldws_B.i++) {



964    if (vipldws_B.uDFIRFilter[vipldws_B.i] > vipldws_P.Saturation_UpperSat) {



965      vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] = vipldws_P.Saturation_UpperSat;



966    } else if (vipldws_B.uDFIRFilter[vipldws_B.i] <



967               vipldws_P.Saturation_LowerSat) {



968      vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] = vipldws_P.Saturation_LowerSat;



969    } else {



970      vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] = vipldws_B.uDFIRFilter[vipldws_B.i];



971    }



972  }



973



974  /* End of Saturate: '<S3>/Saturation' */



975



976  /* S-Function (svipgraythresh): '<S3>/Image thresholding' */



977  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 256; vipldws_B.i++) {



978    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i] = 0.0F;



979    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i] = 0.0F;



980  }



981



982  vipldws_B.scale = 255.0F;



983  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 48000; vipldws_B.i++) {



984    if (vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] < 0.0F) {



985      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[0]++;



986    } else if (vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] > 1.0F) {



987      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[255]++;



988    } else {



989      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[(uint8_T)



990        (vipldws_B.Saturation[vipldws_B.i] * vipldws_B.scale + 0.5F)]++;



991    }



992  }



993



994  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 256; vipldws_B.i++) {



995    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i] /= 48000.0F;



996  }



997



998  vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[0] = vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[0];



999  vipldws_B.cnt = 2.0F;



1000  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 255; vipldws_B.i++) {



1001    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i + 1] =



1002      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i + 1] * vipldws_B.cnt +



1003      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1004    vipldws_B.cnt++;



1005    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i + 1] +=



1006      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1007  }



1008



1009  vipldws_B.cnt = vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[255];



1010  for (vipldws_B.i = 0; vipldws_B.i < 256; vipldws_B.i++) {



1011    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i] =



1012      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i] * vipldws_B.cnt -



1013      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1014    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i] *=



1015      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1016    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i] *= 1.0F -



1017      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1018    vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i] =



1019      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_MU_DW[vipldws_B.i] /



1020      vipldws_DW.Imagethresholding_P_DW[vipldws_B.i];



1021  }



1022

1024  vipldws_B.cnt = 0.0F;
